          <Vi>thuộc Ai Cập, kiểu Ai Cập</Vi>
          <En>relating to Egypt, its people, culture, or language</En>
          <Example>The Egyptian pyramids are among the most famous ancient structures in the world.</Example>
          <IsArchaic>false</IsArchaic>
          <Situations>
            <Situation id="bbdb9f7a-6f0b-4bcb-9267-599f8c5ae24c">
